                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Fugit
                                corporis quas beatae maxime porro repudiandae </div>
                        </div>

                    </section>

                </main>
            </section>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-5 inspo-section d-flex justify-content-center row">
            <section>
                <div class="quote d-flex justify-content-center mb-5">
                    <img src="/assets/quotes-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="quote" width="25px">
                    <span class="mx-4 align-self-center">
                        You go to therapy not for answers, you go for questions, we already have the answers inside of
                        us - Robert Rodriguez
                    </span>
                    <img src="/assets/quotes-end-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="end quote" width="25px">
                </div>

                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-self-center mb-5">
                    <a href="/register" class="text-decoration-none create-acc-btn p-2 px-3 shadow-lg rounded-2">
